---
title: Sticky Date Pudding with Caramel Sauce & Cream | Serves 4+
description: Finish your dinner off with the very best kind of pudding – sticky date! Cakey on top and densely rich underneath, it's studded with chewy dates and topped off with an oozy caramel sauce for an indulgent dessert that never fails to please.
